10. Refund Rate by Product

SQL QUERY
SELECT 
    oi.product_id,
    COUNT(r.refund_id) AS refunds,
    COUNT(oi.order_item_id) AS total_orders,
    COUNT(r.refund_id) / COUNT(oi.order_item_id) AS refund_rate
FROM order_items oi
LEFT JOIN order_item_refunds r
ON oi.order_item_id = r.order_item_id
GROUP BY oi.product_id;
```

Insight:
A lot of products have a disastrous 100% rate while some have a lower percentage.

Business Recommendation:
There should be an immediate de-listing and a deep-dive into supplier's qualit control to prevent further financial and reputational damage.

